<exercise checkit-seed="0001" checkit-slug="AI2" checkit-title="Arc Length">
    <statement>
        <p>
            Consider the curve <m>y=\sqrt{3 \, x + 5}</m> defined on <m>[3, 5]</m>.
            <ol>
                <li>
                    Estimate the arclength of this curve with <m>4</m> line segments with <m>\Delta x = 0.5</m>.
                </li>
                <li>
                    Find an integral that computes the arclength of this curve.
                </li>
            </ol>
        </p>
        
    </statement>
    <answer>
        <p>
            <ol>
                <li>
                    <me>
               \begin{array}{|c|c|c|c|c|}
              \hline
              x_i
              &amp;
              x_{i+1}
              &amp;
              f(x_{i})
              &amp;
              f(x_{i+1})
              &amp;
              \text{Length of segment}          
              \\
              \hline
               3
              &amp; 
               3.5
              &amp;
               3.7417
              &amp; 
               3.937
              &amp;
               0.5368         
                  \\
               3.5
              &amp; 
               4.0
              &amp;
               3.937
              &amp; 
               4.1231
              &amp;
               0.5335         
                  \\
               4.0
              &amp; 
               4.5
              &amp;
               4.1231
              &amp; 
               4.3012
              &amp;
               0.5308         
                  \\
               4.5
              &amp; 
               5.0
              &amp;
               4.3012
              &amp; 
               4.4721
              &amp;
               0.5284         
                  \\
              
              \hline
              \end{array}
          </me>
              The estimated length of this curve is 2.1295.      
                </li>
                <li>
                    The arclength is computed via <me>\int_{ 3 }^{ 5 }\sqrt{1+ \left(\frac{3}{2 \, \sqrt{3 \, x + 5}}\right)^2}dx.</me> 
                </li>
            </ol>
        </p>
    </answer>
</exercise>
